Poetry - Project Setup

Manage dependencies in your Python project with [prgm]poetry[/prgm]. Use the [prgm]add[/prgm] subcommand to add new dependencies.

Create a new project

$ [prgm]poetry new[/prgm] [arg-value]project-name[/arg-value]            # Create new project at <project-name>
$ [prgm]poetry init[/prgm]                        # Create a basic pyproject.toml in the current directory

Installing an existing project

$ [prgm]poetry install[/prgm]                     # Install dependencies, and entrypoints, from pyproject.toml
